    "flaws": [
      {
        "name": "Dark Secret",
        "focus": "Former Sabbat",
        "value": 2,
        "description": "",
        "rules": "",
        "notes": [
          "Caesar's sire, Jervais, sought him out specifically to use as a double agent who could work around the Tremere of the Camarilla while assisting House Goratrix: the Tremere Antitribu. He was an unwitting pawn... at first.",
          "Driven to despair by his role as a catspaw for his sire alongside watching the horrors that took place in the USA over the course of a century made him fully turn to the Sabbat, believing himself forsaken by the Lwa.",
          "Parts of this are known, but this is spun by Caesar as him actually being a double agent for House Tremere against the Sabbat. In fact, he takes credit for assisting in the 1998 ritual that crippled the Sabbat defectors."
        ],
        "source": {
          "book": "",
          "page": 0
        }
      },
      {
        "name": "Groveling Worm",
        "focus": "",
        "value": 2,
        "description": "",
        "rules": "",
        "notes": [
          "In a mix of pleasure and penance he draws more blood than needed for his appeasements to the Lwa."
        ],
        "source": {
          "book": "",
          "page": 0
        }
      },
      {
        "name": "Prey Exclusion",
        "focus": "Mortals",
        "value": 2,
        "description": "",
        "rules": "",
        "notes": "",
        "source": {
          "book": "",
          "page": 0
        }
      },
      {
        "name": "Shunned",
        "focus": "Anarchs",
        "value": 2,
        "description": "",
        "rules": "",
        "notes": [
          "Caesar's reputation for being a \"Blood Leech\" is known and is especially reviled by the Anarchs.",
          "This is exacerbated even further due to him specifically targeting Duskborn and Caitiffs."
        ],
        "source": {
          "book": "",
          "page": 0
        }
      },
      {
        "name": "Folkloric Bane",
        "focus": "Salt",
