        "description": "",
        "rules": "",
        "notes": [
          "Whether because Black Caesar has developed the vulnerabilities of the spirits, or because of his time spent on the open ocean, a barrier of salt represents a psychological obstacle that he must force himself to overcome."
        ],
        "source": {
          "book": "",
          "page": 0
        }
      },
