      {
        "era": "A Time of Dominion",
        "startYear": 1998,
        "endYear": 2025,
        "affiliation": "camarilla",
        "details": "After surviving the Tremere Antitribu's near extinction due to the sacrifice of one of the Lwa bound to him, Caesar's loyalty in the Sabbat wanes as he begins to reattune himself to his prior faith. Making a dangerous journey from the borders of Canada to the States he cashed in his life boon with Mortius of the Milwaukee Chantry to concoct a story claiming his time in the Sabbat was a double agent plot that was masterfully crafted by the Council. When the Prime Chantry falls years later nobody can disprove this fabricated tale. With a hunger to rebuild the now basically defunct House High Saturday he makes his way to Toronto. His masterful infiltration of a Sabbat stronghold, and limited ties to the University Chantry following Scheer's fall made him the top pick for Ulrich's sheriff, a title he assumed in 2020 shortly after Ulrich became Prince. After a few years of loyal service, the Prince granted him the right of Embrace: Severin Koslov, who has since been placed as a ward of the Bleak Bokor to learn the arts of necromancy from the true masters.\n\n\"I know what a city on the brink looks like. Trust me. Toronto needs a firm hand.\"",
        "locations": [
          "Milwaukee, USA",
          "Toronto, Canada"
        ]
      }
